{"tid":1350813,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"請係用\"Fact Checked\"一字之前諗清楚","createTime":"2019-07-22T13:48:45.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-23T08:52:19.000Z","uid":916,"like":169,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":39,"replies":[{"pid":"819d6ab54474073f4e94dca4e1749f556fbdb989","tid":1350813,"uid":916,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T13:48:45.000Z","msg":"自反送中fact check channel成立以來, 我地可以好方便咁掌握實時, 可靠同客觀嘅資訊,<br />\n正因為大家都接收緊呢啲<strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">具廣泛認受性嘅資訊</span></strong>, 抗爭者陣線先可以<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">史無前例地統一</span></strong>, 以呢啲具廣泛認受性嘅資訊作為基礎作出<span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>共識</strong></span>, 甚至唔需要討論, 就可以<strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">各自執行</span></strong>可以達到<strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">共同目標</span></strong>嘅行動, 亦姐係<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">「兄弟爬山, 各有各做」</span></strong>。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">但而家出面好多唔達到「具廣泛認受性」標準嘅消息不斷流傳, 更強調「已證實, fact checked」。請問轉發消息嘅人, 你地有冇思考過呢啲資訊嘅可靠性? 當民眾被唔可靠嘅資訊包圍, 就會失去<span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>達至共識嘅基礎</strong></span>, </span><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><em><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">情況就同2014年金鐘謠言瘋傳一樣。</span></strong></em></span><br />\n<br />\n為左唔令2014嘅失敗再次發生, 我希望大家當發放資訊時都堅守以下原則:<br />\n1. 任何資訊, 都要包含資料來源同時間 (新聞, 一手/二手圖片, TG Channel, 親戚/朋友轉發)<br />\n2. 可信性存疑, 但關乎人身安全嘅資訊, 請強調「未確實」, 由接收者自行判斷<br />\n3. 移除所有不客觀同模糊嘅字眼 (請廣傳/已證實/XX報料) <br />\n<br />\n其實反送中fact check channel 已經做左一個好好嘅例子:<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vqo32L3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fvqo32L3.jpg&h=94ddc1c6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n再睇下一個反面教材, 同埋改正方法:<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6ZjSbEv.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6ZjSbEv.jpg&h=3d6edfd3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tf1Jijw.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ftf1Jijw.jpg&h=f12a0a0c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n總結:<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2DM9dS9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2DM9dS9.jpg&h=96889d94&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n利申: 第一次出長post, 今日都仲有番工嘅垃圾, 淨係識用ppt整啲柒圖。最後好多謝反送中fact check channel (<a href=\"https://t.me/s/antiextraditionverifiednews\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fs%2Fantiextraditionverifiednews&d=h%2FjpO%2F4vOxs1xnBU3UKRHkPclXdXKQfB%2FlJdEd6ZkMI%3D&h=de111f9e\" target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/s/antiextraditionverifiednews</a>), 我好希望每一個香港人都要睇佢個channel。"},{"pid":"956d54d2f8888454bdbd254384788e18ccef6cc9","tid":1350813,"uid":21699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T13:50:27.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"67e02fb4d47ccb5ca028235567ce69603eb18050","tid":1350813,"uid":916,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T13:55:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"795ae3e8e3ce762f1b57eef917252da894d6aa73","tid":1350813,"uid":109154,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T13:56:13.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b4fed6be40d8237d356517369d48b7a6514f0f23","tid":1350813,"uid":5159,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T13:56:21.000Z","msg":"fact check 第一步, 無圖就block, whatsapp/telegram cap 對話都block"},{"pid":"fdb4c6ab8cb419293306b083a1b2624c1526f37f","tid":1350813,"uid":71091,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T13:58:44.000Z","msg":"有用！！ push!!"},{"pid":"143ee385bcd3f02d93a72d4269d57dc0b9962686","tid":1350813,"uid":165683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T14:00:12.000Z","msg":"PUsh"},{"pid":"b88e3b364c67a8bafccb532ac22a249f1e901315","tid":1350813,"uid":257216,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T14:00:38.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"e47934436689e97e48448c7879344ac260596f6c","tid":1350813,"uid":916,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"b4fed6be40d8237d356517369d48b7a